"A lush tan froth stands steady atop this reddish-brown brew.  Smells of persimmon, black grape, molasses and slight vegetal tannins.  Tastes of grain wrapped in notes of grape and plum, grape juice and a pinch of nutmeg.  Easy going down with a very slight alcohol presence, but still quite flavorful."
