"Wow! A very bland and unexciting offering by two breweries that generally offer impressive beers. I don't get this. Little nose or aroma and the flavor is just a tad distinctive with a mostly weak malt body and an overall metallic hop bitterness. Something big and mysterious is missing here, and this winds up being a near total dud when weighed against these two breweries other offerings. Weak and sickly in the grand scheme of things..."
