""
""
"This was excellent.  When two of my favorite breweries got together to make a beer, I knew I wanted to try it, and I finally found a bottle.  It's a great golden ale, not too heavy, very smooth, and I want more.  I've heard the Boulevard version is the one in bottles and is a little maltier, as compared to the Odell version that is on tap and tends to run a little hoppier.  So keep that in mind if you are looking around; they may be slightly different depending on which brewery made it and how you are drinking it.  But either way, this is a beer well worth seeking out, and here's hoping for a 50th Anniversary collaboration!"
