"Overall - I'm not convinced this is an American Strong Ale, but then again I'm not sure how to classify it. Its not any of the pale ale styles, not enough hops. Of course not a porter or stout. So I guess this classification works. The history and story behind this beer and the breweries who collaborated on it is much more interesting than that of the beer itself, although it is certainly worth a try. A bit on the steep price side."
