"Tired this at a beer school event in KC. The founders of Boulevard and Odell's where there talking about their history for two hours. I don't think strong ale is the correct style, more of a ESB with Belgium yeast. The Boulevard beer is a very malty compared to the Odell style ( only on draft) that is considerably more hoppy. I was a little disappointed with both of them but was awesome to hear their passion for two years."
